<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Service & Support | Aspire Packaging</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fdfdfd; color: #333; }
    header {
      background: #8b0000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; }

    .section {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #8b0000;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .support-cards {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .card h3 { color: #8b0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .card p { color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    footer {
      background: #222;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Service & Support</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Customer First, Always</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
      At Aspire Packaging, our commitment doesn't end at the sale. Our nationwide service team ensures that your machines operate smoothly, efficiently, and reliably.
    </p>

    <div class="support-cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Installation Support</h3>
        <p>Get expert assistance with on-site setup and calibration of your machines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Maintenance</h3>
        <p>Scheduled preventive maintenance packages to extend the life of your equipment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Spare Parts</h3>
        <p>We ensure fast and reliable delivery of original spare parts across India.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Remote Assistance</h3>
        <p>Get technical troubleshooting and virtual support anytime, anywhere.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Warranty Claims</h3>
        <p>Easy claim process with genuine support and minimum downtime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Aspire Packaging. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
